---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import ParallaxSection from '../components/ParallaxSection.astro';
import ScrollReveal from '../components/ScrollReveal.astro';
---

<Base title="商业" currentPath="/business">
  <ParallaxSection
    bgImage="/images/business-1.jpg"
    headingZh="温州模式"
    headingEn="The Wenzhou Model"
    dark={true}
    level={1}
  >
    <ScrollReveal>
      <p>以家庭工业和专业化市场为基础，温州人创造了一种自下而上的经济发展模式。小商品、大市场——这是温州模式的精髓所在。</p>
      <p class="en-sub">Built on family workshops and specialized markets — small goods, big markets. The essence of the Wenzhou economic model.</p>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </ParallaxSection>

  <ParallaxSection
    bgImage="/images/business-2.jpg"
    headingZh="全球商业版图"
    headingEn="Global Business Footprint"
  >
    <ScrollReveal>
      <p>温州商会在全球98个国家和地区设有分支机构。从意大利普拉托的纺织业到巴西圣保罗的电子市场，温州人掌控着众多产业链的关键环节。</p>
      <p class="en-sub">Wenzhou business associations operate in 98 countries. From textiles in Prato to electronics in Sao Paulo, Wenzhou entrepreneurs control key supply chain links.</p>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </ParallaxSection>

  <ParallaxSection
    bgImage="/images/business-3.jpg"
    headingZh="新一代企业家"
    headingEn="A New Wave of Entrepreneurs"
    dark={true}
  >
    <ScrollReveal>
      <p>从传统制造到科技创新，新一代温州企业家正在硅谷、深圳和特拉维夫开创未来。他们将温商的务实精神与前沿科技相融合。</p>
      <p class="en-sub">From manufacturing to tech innovation, a new generation blends Wenzhou pragmatism with cutting-edge technology in Silicon Valley, Shenzhen, and Tel Aviv.</p>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </ParallaxSection>
</Base>

<script src="../scripts/parallax.js"></script>
<script src="../scripts/scroll-reveal.js"></script>
